      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR LORD (3) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 2 lengths from the winner Blackpool Viper (22.80) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Likely to feature again. FRANTIC PHYLLIS (1) collided with another runner last time and always well back when sixth (23.78) in a Grade 6 at this track. Worth following up. COOL ASH (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (23.64) in a Grade 6 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. WEST ON ROSE (8) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
